      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d216n1-ptr" id="PJA04d216n1">1</a>
      
   <p>Jonathan Mason (17561831), law student of Josiah Quincy Jr. and later of <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> and Perez Morton, was admitted to the bar in 1779 (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Legal Papers of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. Kinvin Wroth and Hiller B. Zobel, Cambridge, 1965; 3 vols. ]">JA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Legal Papers</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-05-01-01-0012#ADMS-05-01-01-pb-0104" class="pageNo">1:civ</a>).</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d216n2-ptr" id="PJA04d216n2">2</a>
      
   <p>See <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Abigail Adams (17441818), m. John Adams 1764 ]">AA</abbr> to John Thaxter, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-04-02-02-0020" class="document">7 July</a> and <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Abigail Adams (17441818), m. John Adams 1764 ]">AA</abbr> to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-04-02-02-0026" class="document">1314 July</a>, <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Adams Family Correspondence&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1963. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Adams Family Correspondence</span></span>, 2:37, 4548.</p>

